---
const { title, image, description, link } = Astro.props;
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<a href={ link } class="card bg-base-100 w-auto shadow-xl">
    <figure>
      <Image
        src={ image }
        alt="House Image" />
    </figure>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h2 class="card-title">
        { title }
        <div class="badge badge-secondary">NEW</div>
      </h2>
      <p>新千歳空港から電車で40分の好立地。道央の狩猟拠点です。</p>
      <div class="card-actions justify-end">
        <div class="badge badge-outline">北海道</div>
        <div class="badge badge-outline">車あり</div>
        <div class="badge badge-outline">ガンロッカー</div>
      </div>
    </div>
</a>